column5: Got down to the last day and took this button Buck. Pepperetts for the Boys at Quinte next week
Congrats on the successful hunt FF.  Pepperettes be sounding mighty good!
WTG Dave, the ones that size are better eating anyway.
Venison for the table. Good shooting !
Awesome Dave    Congrats Some good eats right there Leechman
Congrats to you Dave! Drop shot eh?
OLD MAN ay, the board swear censor didn't pick that word up, very vulgar.  Thats a different way to put it Roy  Thanks everyone
